  "description": "<p>Job Title: Class 4 Driver (Catering Company)<br />Location: Tuas<br />Working Hours:</p><p>• 6 days per week<br />• Shift-based (roster system):<br />o 5:00 AM – 2:00 PM<br />o 1:00 PM – 10:00 PM<br />• Shifts rotate monthly (e.g. morning shift this month, afternoon shift next month)</p><p>Transportation:<br />• For 5:00 AM shift: Company driver will pick you up from your residential block<br />• For 1:00 PM shift: Company transport provided from Joo Koon MRT<br />• Company vehicle cannot be driven home<br />• Driving a 12-ft lorry</p><p>Work Schedule:<br />• Saturday and Sunday required<br />• Rest day on a weekday</p><p>Salary:<br />• Up to $3,600</p><p>Benefits:<br />• Variable Bonus (VB)<br />• Annual Leave: 14 days</p><p>Job Description:<br />• Delivery of food, staff, and related items</p><p>Requirements:<br />• Must possess a valid Class 4 driving licence</p>",
